reviewText: Being a cat lover, I received the Jingle Cats CD as a gag gift at work one Christmas. When I played it at home, my cats went nuts trying to find these cats that were "singing". Now with the DVD we can all see these sweet little kitties wishing everyone a Merry Christmas!
Silent Night was the best Christmas carol of the video because it's the most realistic. The others sounded like the Chipmunks.
